manager electronic chemicals division    air products  chemicals inc company overview air products touches the lives of consumers around the globe in positive ways every day with over  employees and operations in more than  countries we serve customers across a wide range of industries from food and beverage health and personal care to energy transportation and semiconductors we supply a unique portfolio of atmospheric gases process and specialty gases performance materials equipment and services founded in  air products has built a reputation for its innovative culture operational excellence and commitment to safety and the environment our aim is to develop lasting relationships with our customers and communities based on human qualities understanding their needs doing business with integrity and honesty and demonstrating a passion for exceeding expectations boards  committees corporate boards ▾ lead director board of directors   current kmg chemicals inc kmg chemicals inc manufactures and distributes specialty chemicals it operates through the following segments electronic chemicals wood treating chemicals and industrial lubricants the electronic chemicals segment sells wet process chemicals primarily to the semiconductor industry these are used to clean and etch silicon wafers in the production of semiconductors the wood treating chemicals segment produces and supplies pentachlorophenol a specialty chemical for industrial wood treating applications the industrial lubricants segment provide products and services for industrial valve and actuator maintenance this segment product portfolio includes valve lubricants cleaners and sealants as well as related products such as fittings adapters and application equipment the company was founded in  and is headquartered fort worth tx independent nonexecutive director    az electronic materials sa az electronic materials sa develops and manufactures antireflective coatings and ancillary chemicals which are used in integrate